omment_count":0,"description":"\u003cp\u003eLoop analysis is a key component of static analysis tools. Unfortunately, there are several rare edge cases. As a tool moves from academic prototype to production-ready, obscure cases can and do occur. This results in loop analysis being a key source of late-discovered but significant algorithmic bugs. To avoid these, this paper presents a collection of examples and “folklore” challenges in loop analysis.\u003c/p\u003e\n","description_plain":"Loop analysis is a key component of static analysis tools. Unfortunately, there are several rare edge cases. As a tool moves from academic prototype to production-ready, obscure cases can and do occur. This results in loop analysis being a key source of late-discovered but significant algorithmic bugs. To avoid these, this paper presents a collection of examples and “folklore” challenges in loop analysis.","submitter_user":"allie","user_is_author":false,"tags":["c","pdf","performance"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zga4q7","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/zga4q7/misconceptions_about_loops_c_2024"},{"short_id":"knrrsr","created_at":"2026-07-15T01:03:23.197-05:00","title":"How C++20 improved the for-loop syntax","url":"https://lzon.ca/posts/tips/cpp-for-range-init/","score":17,"flags":0,"comment_count":12,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"raymii","user_is_author":false,"tags":["c++"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/knrrsr","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/knrrsr/how_c_20_improved_for_loop_syntax"},{"short_id":"idjph9","created_at":"2026-07-15T01:01:22.584-05:00","title":"The Prompt-Wait-Evaluate Loop: How AI Kills Flow Without You Noticing","url":"https://www.sandordargo.com/blog/2026/07/15/how-ai-kills-flow","score":0,"flags":1,"comment_count":0,"description":"","description_plain":"","submitter_user":"raymii","user_is_author":false,"tags":["vibecoding"],"short_id_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/idjph9","comments_url":"https://lobste.rs/s/idjph9/prompt